  "description": "A wide-angle shot showcases a grey and overcast seascape dominated by the distant, iconic Golden Gate Bridge. The bridge, painted in a vibrant orange, stretches across the waterway, partially obscured by low-hanging grey clouds. The water is choppy and dark blue-grey, with small rock formations visible near the foreground. Dark green vegetation, likely coastal shrubs, occupies the extreme right edge of the frame, providing a subtle foreground element. The background reveals rolling hills and mountains, also shrouded in grey mist, creating a sense of depth and distance. The overall scene is cool-toned and atmospheric.",
